---

<PageLayout
  title="Industry Leaders"
  description="Meet the industry leaders speaking at CoreCon 2025"
  heroTitle="Industry Leaders"
  heroSubtitle="Learn from executives and technical directors who are shaping the future of technology"
>
  <div class="speakers-container">
    <div class="speakers-intro">
      <p>Our industry leaders track features CTOs, VPs of Engineering, Research Directors, and other technology executives who bring strategic perspective and extensive experience to CoreCon. These leaders will share insights on technology strategy, organizational challenges, and emerging trends that are shaping the industry.</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Category Links -->
    <div class="category-links">
      {categories.map(category => (
        <a 
          href={category.link} 
          class={`category-link ${category.id === 'industry' ? 'active' : ''}`}
        >
          {category.name}
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
    
    <!-- Speakers Grid -->
    <div class="speakers-grid">
      {industryLeaders.map(speaker => (
        <SpeakerCard {...speaker} />
      ))}
    </div>
    
    <!-- Topics Section -->
    <div class="topics-section">
      <h2>Industry Leader Topics</h2>
      <div class="topics-grid">
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Technology Strategy</h3>
          <p>Aligning technology choices with business objectives and navigating the complex landscape of options and trade-offs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Scaling Engineering Organizations</h3>
          <p>Building and maintaining effective engineering teams through periods of growth and technology transformation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Technical Leadership</h3>
          <p>Balancing technical depth with leadership responsibilities and guiding technical direction at scale.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Emerging Technologies</h3>
          <p>Evaluating and adopting emerging technologies with a strategic perspective on business impact and implementation challenges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .speakers-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .speakers-intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .speakers-intro p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }
  
  /* Category Links */
  .category-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary-light);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
  }
  
  .category-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  
  .category-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent-dark);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .category-link.active {
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  /* Speakers Grid */
  .speakers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  /* SpeakerCard component styling enhancements */
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-card) {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-card:hover) {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-image) {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 250px;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-image img) {
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-card:hover .speaker-image img) {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-image::after) {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7), transparent);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-content) {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-name) {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-role) {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-company) {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-bio) {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tags) {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tag) {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  /* Alternate tag colors */
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tag:nth-child(3n+1)) {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tag:nth-child(3n+2)) {
    background-color: var(--color-secondary-light);
    color: var(--color-secondary-dark);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tag:nth-child(3n+3)) {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent-dark);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-tag:hover) {
    filter: brightness(0.95);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.speaker-social) {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.social-link) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    background-color: var(--color-background-alt);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.social-link:hover) {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.social-link[data-platform="twitter"]:hover) {
    background-color: #1DA1F2;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.social-link[data-platform="linkedin"]:hover) {
    background-color: #0A66C2;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .speakers-grid :global(.social-link[data-platform="github"]:hover) {
    background-color: #24292e;
    color: white;
  }
  
  /* Topics Section */
  .topics-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
  }
  
  .topics-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-accent-dark);
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .topics-section h2::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  
  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .topic-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 4px solid;
  }
  
  .topic-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  /* Color-code each topic card */
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+1) {
    border-top-color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+2) {
    border-top-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+3) {
    border-top-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+4) {
    border-top-color: var(--color-success);
  }
  
  .topic-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Match heading color to card border color */
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+1) h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+2) h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary-dark);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+3) h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent-dark);
  }
  
  .topic-card:nth-child(4n+4) h3 {
    color: var(--color-success);
  }
  
  .topic-card p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* Responsive Styles */
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .speakers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    
    .topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .speakers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .category-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .category-link {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .topics-section {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>